{"tid":1915103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百人金鐘悼梁凌杰生忌","createTime":"2020-03-08T03:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T03:48:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56cb5a3a155c1c38a2df43b993f57462486ff637","tid":1915103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/5P2VYURM7OJVSJBG5HKV6DJNNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2F5P2VYURM7OJVSJBG5HKV6DJNNI%2F&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=81705bea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2F5P2VYURM7OJVSJBG5HKV6DJNNI%2F&h=db979d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/5P2VYURM7OJVSJBG5HKV6DJNNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n百人金鐘悼梁凌杰生忌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200308/large/1583599154_9a8a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200308%2Flarge%2F1583599154_9a8a.gif&h=3981553e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一對母女在梁凌杰花壇獻花。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動怒火也許不再熾熱，但港人從沒忘記運動中殞落的抗爭者。去年6月15日，梁凌杰穿着背上寫有「林鄭殺港 黑警冷血」的黃色雨衣，站在金鐘太古廣場四樓平台，失足墮地後不治。<br />\n<br />\n昨日是梁凌杰的生忌，民間發起悼念活動，約200人攜白色鮮花和蠟燭到太古廣場紀念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200308/large/1583599154_d933.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200308%2Flarge%2F1583599154_d933.gif&h=b53e69c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾百人到金鐘太古廣場外悼念梁凌杰的生忌。"}]}